                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="exhibition"></a>Public exhibition of plans for a new care home. Friday 11th October</a></h3>
                <p>To be held in All Saints small hall, Onslow Gardens, CR2 9AB. Friday 11th October, 3 - 7 pm.</p>
                <p>Churchgate services are putting on a public exhibition for a chance to find out more about their proposals to build a new 60 bed care home on the corner of Sanderstead Hill and Addington Road.</p>
